		(property "Description" "The R1LP5256E Series is a family of low voltage 256-Kbit static RAMs organized as 32, 768-word by 8-bit, fabricated by Renesass high-performance 0. 15um CMOS and TFT technologies. The R1LP5256E Series has realized higher density, higher performance and low power consumption. The R1LP5256E Series is suitable for memory applications where a simple interfacing, battery operating and battery backup are the important design objectives. It has been packaged in 28-pin SOP and 28-pin TSOP."
